      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CARRY ON MACI (8) goes very well this trip starting 15 times for eight wins and four minors. Below best last time at Warragul (22.88) in a Special conditions H, finishing a 4 length fifth. Appeals as a leading chance in this. THORKILDSEN (2) has been without a win for a while, the latest jumping from an outside draw when fourth (16.92) at Healesville in a Grade 4/5. Has a good record at this journey. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Can do much better this time. MAX PEARL (1) quickly away to win over the 390m at Warrnambool two runs back then settled forward again when finishing second at Warragul last start. Has performed well from this box with a win and three minor placings to her name from five starts. Hard to beat again.",
